00:06:04.070 --> 00:06:06.069
And for now,
that man is<i> El Presidente.</i>

00:06:06.070 --> 00:06:08.799
Well, killing<i> El Presidente</i>
would change all that.

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:11.270
You guys are crazy.

00:06:12.340 --> 00:06:15.209
What are you,
Defense Intelligence?

00:06:15.210 --> 00:06:16.340
CIA?

00:06:16.350 --> 00:06:20.550
Yeah, you guys are crazy.

00:06:22.150 --> 00:06:25.620
<i>Adiós,</i> Marco.

00:06:38.030 --> 00:06:39.229
I got to go!

00:06:39.230 --> 00:06:41.430
